data.description: Excellently maintained two story home in Universal City.  Spacious floorplan with two living areas downstairs plus a loft upstairs.  Huge kitchen with center island and build in desk area.  Master bedroom complete with en-suite bathroom with separate tub and shower, double vanities, and walk in closet.  Additional generously sized bedrooms give you plenty of room for the whole family.  Close to major highways, dining, and entertainment.  WELCOME HOME!!
